_sText:
This is NAV-file for tactic, fun and simple map [de_tuscan](http://css.gamebanana.com/maps/158440 "").


So, bots using all possible ways now. Also added detailed place names, so you'll always know from bots, where the enemies are.


I would like to note one thing: when bots are trying to go down the ladder into the tunnel, if you are passing close - break the boards, which close passage, because bots don't do it (I do not know why), and therefore can not come down so long as the passage is closed.

Have fun! ;D

	UPDATE 12.07.2014:
	Now bots destroying boards without problems. Thanks to Meurglis3 for it
